Package com.example.cshare.ui.viewmodels

Contains ViewModel classes designed to store and manage UI-related data in a lifecycle conscious way.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the authentication-related data for an Activity or a Fragment.
    CartViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the list of in cart products data for the CartFragment and the HomeScreenActivity
    HomeViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the list of available products data for the HomeScreenActivity and the HomeFragment.
    ProductViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the product operations-related data for an Activity or a Fragment.
    ProfileViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the profile-related data for an Activity or a Fragment.
    SharedViewModel
    ViewModel class responsible for preparing and managing the list of in cart products data for the HomeScreenActivity or the SharedFragment.

Package com.example.cshare.ui.viewmodels Description
